# Rope Data Structure Module (Facade)
# Efficient string manipulation using tree-based rope structure
# Provides O(log n) operations for large text documents
#
# This module serves as a facade, re-exporting all rope functions
# from categorized submodules for a clean public API.

# ============================================================================
# MODULE STRUCTURE
# ============================================================================
# - types.spl:      Type definitions, constants, and type predicates
# - create.spl:     Rope creation and cloning operations
# - concat.spl:     Concatenation and merging operations
# - split.spl:      Splitting and chunking operations
# - search.spl:     Search, comparison, and indexing operations
# - modify.spl:     Modification operations (insert, delete, replace)
# - balance.spl:    Rebalancing and optimization operations
# - utilities.spl:  Conversion, iteration, formatting, and validation utilities

# ============================================================================
# EXPORTS
# ============================================================================
# All functions are re-exported from their respective modules.
# Import this module to access the complete rope API.
